Maintainer: Wayne D. Ndlovu <waynedndlovu5@gmail.com>
Description: The `easyrbi` package houses multiple functions that allow the user to download streamflow data from the USGS website and perform MannKendall and sens.slope analysis on calculated annual Richards-Baker Flashiness Index (RBI) values.
